Text: Note: This is the complete collection from http://andreasviklund.com/ as of September 15th. Future releases and add-on material can be found on http://andreasviklund.com/templates/
Note: The actual number is 19 templates. The template called "Daleri Clean" should not have been included as it is an old and unfinished version of "Variant Classic".
Wow! These templates are really good! Keep 'em coming!
